Use the standard library
This is how to sort_third of l:
  Remember that result is []
  Remember that i is 0
  Do this l's length times:
    When remainder of i and 3 is 0, then:
      Remember that smallest_index is i
      Remember that j is sum of i and 3
      Do this l's length times:
        When j is less than l's length, then:
          When item j in l is less than item smallest_index in l, then:
            Remember that smallest_index is j
          End when
          Remember that j is sum of j and 3
        But, if not:
          Leave the loop
        End when
      End do
      Add result to item smallest_index in l
    But, if not:
      Add result to item i in l
    End when
    Increase i
  End do
  The answer is result
Now you know